source.name: Campaign Finance - FPPC Form 460 - Schedule C - Non-Monetary Contributions
source.description:
This dataset includes all itemized non-monetary contributions ($100 or more) e-filed on Fair Political Practices Commission (FPPC) Form 460 Schedule "C" Non-Monetary Contributions from 1998 to the present.

The data is current as of the last modified date on this dataset.

See the data key for column definitions:  https://data.sfgov.org/Ethics/Campaign-Finance-Data-Key/wygs-cc76
